{"tid":2098712,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"咁既情況 我call忠勇毅","createTime":"2020-07-07T16:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T21:47:33.000Z","uid":283071,"like":116,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bbc0862da8cff119e3d9297436be07fcaa019578","tid":2098712,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T16:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32v4Waq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32v4Waq.png&h=bb5f009f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以上為網上圖片 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係北角馬寶道成日有人用膠櫈霸車位<br />\n想話擺一擺低架車 去對面買碗外賣都唔得<br />\n次次都係咁 咁我打算call忠勇毅掃鳩佢地<br />\n大家一齊唔好泊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知家父家母話我唔岩<br />\n仲話根本幾十年前d人已經係咁霸<br />\n咁樣會累到其他車都俾人抄牌<br />\n做人要將心比心 如果我係其中一架車 <br />\n無啦啦咁俾人抄牌 你會點？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喂大佬....真係我唔岩咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家邊個話霸霸下就係先？<br />\n一開始咁霸就係唔岩咖啦！<br />\n你地唔出聲 我去糾正就係我錯？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正評:樓主好波！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />負評:樓主老豆老母好家教！"},{"pid":"dc471c2c38b71123085e49921fd96d14c7bdae8d","tid":2098712,"uid":277186,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T16:29:31.000Z","msg":"係藍店就報狗 黃店就由佢"},{"pid":"b45c60b959b83973be56b2ab429e80418c54707a","tid":2098712,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc471c2c38b71123085e49921fd96d14c7bdae8d","tid":2098712,"uid":277186,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T16:29:31.000Z","msg":"係藍店就報狗 黃店就由佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T16:31:03.000Z","msg":"當時係北角馬寶道 <br />\n個邊好多鋪頭d人都講野唔正既阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02464968e6aae076c7d2e6de82dd0c8ae1c504de","tid":2098712,"uid":38047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T16:33:01.000Z","msg":"報佢老母攬抄啦，條街阿公嘅。<br />